Class SimpleKeyTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.adorsys.keymanagement.keyrotation.config.properties.keys.SimpleKeyTemplate

  • public class SimpleKeyTemplate
extends Object
    Key template that allows you to set i.e. key size for encrypting key. I.e. key-templates: secret: algo: AES size: 128 maps to secret key with AES and size 128
